{"text_id":122210,"tokens":["Behaviour","al"," economists"," have"," shown"," that"," people"," are"," often"," averse"," to"," inequality"," and"," will"," make"," choices"," to"," avoid"," unequal"," outcomes","."," In"," this"," paper",","," we"," consider"," how"," to"," allocate"," indiv","isible"," goods"," fairly"," when"," the"," beneficiaries"," have"," a"," preference"," for"," equality","."," In"," particular",","," we"," study"," two"," settings"," that"," are"," commonly"," encountered"," in"," the"," literature",":"," (","1",")"," those"," in"," which"," each"," beneficiary"," has"," a"," unit"," demand"," and"," there"," is"," a"," single"," item"," to"," be"," allocated",";"," and"," (","2",")"," those"," in"," which"," there"," are"," several"," items"," to"," be"," allocated"," and"," each"," beneficiary"," has"," a"," ","1","N"," demand"," function","."," We"," show"," that"," the"," envy","-","free"," allocation"," of"," indiv","isible"," goods"," cannot"," be"," guaranteed"," if"," people"," have"," a"," preference"," for"," equality","."," We"," also"," prove"," that"," an"," envy","-","free"," allocation"," can"," be"," guaranteed"," only"," when"," the"," number"," of"," items"," is"," very"," large"," in"," the"," second"," setting","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"text-davinci-002","label":1}